    "The model's documented accuracy is 97%.",
    "Due to the smaller amount of training samples, the class labeled as \"Moderate Demented\" exhibits the lowest accuracy score; other classes vary similarly.",
    "Also, the training epoch is very less.",
    "Further, Bringas et al. (2020) developed a DL model for identifying the AD stages employing mobility data of patients.",
    "The methodology consists of two distinct phases: (i) a pre-processing phase that reduces the length of accelerometer data sequences and ensures uniform intervals between data points for improved data consistency."
